                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How know it from a Summer's Day?</l>
                    <l>It's Fervors are as firm --</l>
                    <l>And nothing in the Countenance</l>
                    <l>But scintillates the same --</l>
                    <l>Yet Birds examine it and flee --</l>
                    <l>And Vans without a name</l>
                    <l>Inspect the Admonition</l>
                    <l>And sunder as they came --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
